source.name: Campaign Finance Filings Submitted to the New York State Board of Elections: Beginning 1999
source.description: This dataset contains all financial disclosure reports filed with the New York State Board of Elections from July of 1999 through April 15th, 2013. For updated information, please visit http://www.elections.ny.gov
